OL,3,CPensioner who 'horrifically' exploited
OL,4,Cyoung women to line pockets jailed
OL,6,FA pensioner who exploited vulnerable
OL,7,Fyoung women by supplying them with
OL,8,Fheroin in exchange for them working as
OL,9,Fprostitutes has been handed a seven-
OL,10,Fyear sentence.
OL,12,FOliver James MacCormack, 71, was
OL,13,Fsentenced at Belfast Crown Court on
OL,14,FThursday morning having previously
OL,15,Fpleaded guilty to 40 offences, which
OL,16,Fincluded charges of human trafficking
OL,17,Fand controlling prostitution.
