OL,6,FHe also admitted a charge of
OL,7,Fperverting the course of justice,
OL,8,Fwitness intimidation and offences of
OL,9,Fsupplying class A drugs.
OL,11,FThere were nine victims involved in
OL,12,Fthe case, some as young as 17 at the
OL,13,Ftime of the offences. One has since
OL,14,Fdied.
OL,16,FPassing sentence, Judge Gordon Kerr
OL,17,Fsaid MacCormack, whose address was
OL,18,Fgiven as Maghaberry prison, used drugs
OL,19,Fas a means to control his victims.
