OL,6,FSeveral other men have already been
OL,7,Fsentenced as part of the same
OL,8,Finvestigation.
OL,10,FA police officer has described the
OL,11,F"horrific exploitation" of victims
OL,12,Ffollowing the sentencing of MacCormack.
OL,14,FDetective Inspector Rachel Miskelly
OL,15,Fsaid MacCormack targeted nine female
OL,16,Fvictims, supplying them with drugs
OL,17,Fensuring they became dependent upon
OL,18,Fhim for their supply of heroin.
