OL,3,CPensioner who 'horrifically' exploited
OL,4,Cyoung women to line pockets jailed
OL,6,F"This horrific exploitation has
OL,7,Fhappened by local men and on our own
OL,8,Fdoorsteps. They lined their pockets at
OL,9,Fthe expense of young women while using
OL,10,Fthem for their own sexual
OL,11,Fgratification. The girls have been
OL,12,Fused, controlled and treated
OL,13,Fappallingly.
OL,15,F"It's hard for most of us to truly
OL,16,Fimagine what trauma these girls have
OL,17,Fendured."
OL,19,FShe also paid tribute to the
OL,20,F"tremendous courage that the victims
OL,21,Fhave shown".
