OL,6,F"These young women have been
OL,7,Finspirational and I truly hope that
OL,8,Fothers who may be suffering will be
OL,9,Fencouraged to come forward," she said.
OL,11,F"I promise you that we are here to
OL,12,Flisten and to help you, and to bring
OL,13,Fthose who would seek to use and abuse
OL,14,Fto justice.
OL,16,F"I'm also asking others to be mindful
OL,17,Fof the tell-tale signs of human
OL,18,Ftrafficking. This isn't something you
OL,19,Fcan ignore, and if you see or hear any
OL,20,Factivity that causes you concern,
OL,21,Fplease contact us on 101."
